    rdfs:comment 'Channel or mechanism through which the compliance incident was discovered. [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: internal_audit|external_audit|regulatory_inspection|whistleblower|customer_complaint|supplier_audit|self_disclosure — 7 candidates stripped; promote to reference product]' ;
