    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to sustainability.sustainability_initiative. Business justification: Corrective action plans often require sustainability investments (wastewater treatment systems, energy-efficient equipment, chemical substitution). Linking enables tracking remediation as sustainabili' ;
