    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to workforce.employee. Business justification: SLA account manager negotiates carrier/3PL contracts and monitors performance. Required for accountability in vendor management, performance reviews, and escalation workflows in apparel logistics oper' ;
    rdfs:domain ind:SlaAgreement ;
