    rdfs:comment 'The primary social media platform where the influencer has the largest following and engagement. [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: instagram|tiktok|youtube|facebook|twitter|pinterest|snapchat — 7 candidates stripped; promote to reference product]' ;
