    rdfs:comment 'Format of content to be created by the influencer (reel, story, post, blog, video, carousel, live stream). [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: reel|story|post|blog|video|carousel|live_stream — 7 candidates stripped; promote to reference product]' ;
